{{mid}}
{{bottom}}

===Etymology 2===
{{L.}} ''[[peregrinatus]]'', "having travelled abroad", past participle of ''[[peregrinari]]''.

====Adjective====
'''peregrinate'''
# Having traveled; foreign, exotic.

